OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP in court
OL,4,Caccused of harassing ex-wife
OL,6,FA former Conservative MP for Bridgend
OL,7,Fhas appeared in court, accused of
OL,8,Fharassing her ex-wife.
OL,10,FKatie Wallis, formerly known as Jamie
OL,11,FWallis, was MP for Bridgend between
OL,12,F2019 and 2024.
OL,14,FThe ex-politician attended Cardiff
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court and entered a plea
OL,16,Fof not guilty to harassment.
